Description: shared libraries for the CTK+ syntax highlighting widget
 CtkSourceView is a text widget that extends the standard CTK+ 3.x text widget
 CtkTextView. It improves CtkTextView by implementing syntax highlighting and
 other features typical of a source editor.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries required by applications to use
 this widget.

